text: Ilchino () is a rural locality (a selo) and the administrative center of Ilchinsky Selsoviet, Uchalinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 1,143 as of 2010. There are 25 streets. == Geography == It is located 20 km from Uchaly. == References == Category:Rural localities in Uchalinsky District
title: Ilchino
